            "name": "Ecology",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Environment</b> any oceans or coastlines<br/><b>Organization</b> solitary, pair, or gang (3\u20138)<br/><b>Treasure</b> NPC gear (leather armor, falchion, masterwork dagger, other treasure)"
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "The average pirate is a free-spirited renegade who would have great difficulty surviving in the cultured depths of polite, civilized society. Rogues and fighters typically make up the majority of a pirate ship\u2019s crew of sailors, as they possess both the skill and brawn necessary for day-to-day raids and heists. These colorful, adventurous characters chafe at society\u2019s laws and restrictions, and the exciting life of the buccaneer is well suited to pirates\u2019 ferocious independence."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>This rugged character is clad in colorful, mismatched clothing, his hair tied back in a bandana.</i>",
